data.text: @EU_Commission @ECDC_EU Please make sure if Americans etc can come to Europe we should we able to go there too not just one way? When will be finally allowed to travel non essential to safe countries like United States canada etc?????

@EU_Commission @EUCouncil PM Abiy Ahmed has led a brutal crackdown on the country’s many ethnic groups, particularly the Oromos, political parties were forced out of the elections, even though Oromia is the country’s largest voting constituency. #ShamEthiopianElection

@EU_Commission “Eritrean soldiers killed 19 civilians in the latest Tigray atrocity, locals claim. Killings took place near Ethiopia’s Abuna Yemata church on 8 May, according to multiple testimonies” – The Guardian #ShamEthiopianElection #HandsOnEthiopia  #UnitedAgainstAbiy

@EU_Commission @EUCouncil At Ayder Hospital, 430 women have been treated for rape, but thousands more have been assaulted. How can elections happen when citizens are being brutally violated. #ShamEthiopianElection #UnitedAgainstAbiy

@EU_Commission PM Abiy claims that he can continue the war in Oromia because global leaders are not pointing the kind of attention they are pointing at Tigray. We need the international community to expand attention to other regions outside of Tigray. #UnitedAgainstAbiy
